35 such adjudication was made, and the sentence imposed. Any form document to authorize
36 the release of records which is provided by a school to a transferring student or such
37 student's parent or legal guardian shall include a list of class A designated felony acts or
38 class B designated felony acts. The student or his or her parent or legal guardian shall also
39 disclose on the document whether the student is currently serving a suspension or expulsion
40 from another school, the reason for such discipline, and the term of such discipline. If a
41 student so conditionally admitted is found to be ineligible for enrollment pursuant to the
